{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775850971931,"sessionID":"ses_287094653ffeq64otm07rua5jS","part":{"id":"prt_d78f727a20011GAqTn9zDBdimc","messageID":"msg_d78f70407001lfiLvAxD0I5P2y","sessionID":"ses_287094653ffeq64otm07rua5jS","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_a76f5521dea2498aababd30b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 Tasks\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发 |\n| Module | `pkg/router` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Design Stage | ST-0 (Pending) |\n\n---\n\n## Atomic Tasks\n\n### Phase 1: JWT Types and Claims\n\n- [ ] **TASK-001**: Define JWT claim structures\n- [ ] **TASK-002**: Define token types and constants\n- [ ] **TASK-003**: Create JWT configuration structure\n\n### Phase 2: JWT Signing\n\n- [ ] **TASK-010**: Implement JWT signer initialization\n- [ ] **TASK-011**: Implement access token signing\n- [ ] **TASK-012**: Implement refresh token signing\n\n### Phase 3: JWT Verification\n\n- [ ] **TASK-020**: Implement token verification logic\n- [ ] **TASK-021**: Implement claims validation\n- [ ] **TASK-022**: Implement token expiration check\n\n### Phase 4: Token Management\n\n- [ ] **TASK-030**: Implement token refresh mechanism\n- [ ] **TASK-031**: Implement token revocation\n- [ ] **TASK-032**: Implement token blacklisting\n\n### Phase 5: Middleware Integration\n\n- [ ] **TASK-040**: Create JWT authentication middleware\n- [ ] **TASK-041**: Integrate with router handlers\n\n### Phase 6: Testing\n\n- [ ] **TEST-001**: Write unit tests for JWT signing\n- [ ] **TEST-002**: Write unit tests for JWT verification\n- [ ] **TEST-003**: Write integration tests\n- [ ] **TEST-004**: Write performance benchmarks\n\n### Phase 7: Documentation\n\n- [ ] **DOC-001**: Add godoc comments\n- [ ] **DOC-002**: Document configuration options\n- [ ] **DOC-003**: Update module README\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] JWT tokens can be signed with configurable algorithms\n- [ ] JWT tokens can be verified and validated\n- [ ] Token expiration is enforced\n- [ ] Token refresh mechanism works correctly\n- [ ] Authentication middleware integrates with router\n- [ ] All unit tests pass with ≥85% coverage\n- [ ] Performance benchmarks meet requirements\n- [ ] Documentation is complete\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Source | Usage |\n|------------|--------|-------|\n| `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` | External | JWT library |\n| `pkg/router` (AR-009) | Internal | Router base module |\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Order\n\n```\nTASK-001 → TASK-002 → TASK-003 → TASK-010 → TASK-011 → TASK-012\n                                              ↓\n                              TASK-020 → TASK-021 → TASK-022\n                                              ↓\n                              TASK-030 → TASK-031 → TASK-032\n                                              ↓\n                              TASK-040 → TASK-041\n                                              ↓\n                              TEST-001 → TEST-002 → TEST-003 → TEST-004\n                                              ↓\n                              DOC-001 → DOC-002 → DOC-003\n```\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-011/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-011/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-011/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775850971916,"end":1775850971928}}}}
